          <p>
            Dialectic (MuDG) was built on the belief that the future of learning isn't linear—it's networked. While traditional AI assistants offer ephemeral exchanges, we aim to transform interactions into persistent, evolving mind maps that mirror how human curiosity naturally branches and connects.
          </p>

          <p>
            Our philosophy is simple:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li>
              <strong>Speed matters:</strong>
              We optimize for cognitive flow by minimizing technical friction.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Simplicity enables depth:</strong>
              A clean interface allows deeper engagement with complex ideas.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Persistence creates value:</strong>
              Unlike fleeting chats, mind maps accumulate insights over time.
            </li>
          </ul>

          <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200 text-sm text-center">
